    LEFT JOIN [TransmisionType] AS [x.TransmisionType0] ON [x0].[TransmisionTypeId] = [x.TransmisionType0].[Id]
    WHERE [x0].[IsDeleted] <> 1
) AS [t] ON [x.Booking].[CarId] = [t].[Id]
ORDER BY [t].[Id]" (0723d8ff)
